'''共濟失調'''（{{lang-en|Ataxia}}）是指缺乏規律，或者為笨拙，為一種神經疾病上的特徵。失調可以廣泛指在[[中樞神經系統|中樞神經系統]]、[[周圍神經系統|周圍神經系統]]任何其中一環出狀況所表現的病徵，例如掌管[[運動|運動]]和[[平衡|平衡]]的[[小腦|小腦]]。國際共濟失調意識日為九月二十五日<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ataxia.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/2018-IAAD-Awareness-Campaign-Toolkit.pdf|title=International Ataxia Awareness Day|publisher=National Ataxia Foundation|date=2018|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210814064303/https://www.ataxia.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/2018-IAAD-Awareness-Campaign-Toolkit.pdf|archivedate=2021|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rcslt.org/wp-content/uploads/media/September-2020.pdf|title=September 2020 Awareness Events|publisher=Royal College of Speech and Language Therapists|date=2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210814064834/https://www.rcslt.org/wp-content/uploads/media/September-2020.pdf|archivedate=2021|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.lomondpractice.co.uk/website/F20606/files/Events%20calendar%20LR%200321.pdf|title=Calendar of health events|publisher=Lomond Practice|date=2021|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210814064404/https://www.lomondpractice.co.uk/website/F20606/files/Events%20calendar%20LR%200321.pdf|archivedate=2021|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

==種類==
*小腦
*[[前庭系統|前庭系統]]
*感覺神經

==病因==
*缺乏[[維他命B12|維他命B12]]、[[維他命B1|維他命B1]]
*遺傳性失調
*[[肝豆狀核變性|肝豆狀核變性]]
*酒精性小腦萎縮

